  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This ERC proposes a standard interface for social recovery of smart contract accounts. It separates identity and policy verification from the recovery process, allowing more ways to authenticate (known as Guardians) than just on-chain accounts. It also lets users customize recovery policies without changing the account\u2019s smart contract.",
  "title": "Social Recovery Interface"
